name: The Origin Space of ‘The Thing’
description:
A dark art event that provides - with great risk - the origin space of 'The Thing'; it was the disruption of the generative force in Castle Gormenghast, now known to be a subtle fracture of "The Fabric", which provided the energy needed for the creation of 'The Thing'

It is not yet known how that happened - whatever, or whomever, had the level of skill necessary for the act to be cast and then hidden, isn't, at present, unmasked

Totems from both sides - Disruptive and Generative - are currently being read



PNG 7000 x 4328  ||  October 21st 2021  ||  Created by Dark Art Studio in collaboration with AI and multiple threads of a neural network
